.TH "nvme_init_resv_release" 9 "nvme_init_resv_release" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_resv_release \- Initialize passthru command for Reservation Release
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_resv_release
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_resv_rrela rrela "  ","
.BI "bool iekey "  ","
.BI "bool disnsrs "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_resv_rtype rtype "  ","
.BI "__u64 crkey "  ","
.BI "__le64 *payload "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace identifier
.IP "rrela" 12
Reservation release action, see \fIenum nvme_resv_rrela\fP
.IP "iekey" 12
Set to ignore the existing key
.IP "disnsrs" 12
Disperse Namespace Reservation Support
.IP "rtype" 12
The type of reservation to be create, see \fIenum nvme_resv_rtype\fP
.IP "crkey" 12
The current reservation key to release
.IP "payload" 12
Data payload buffer to hold crkey
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Reservation Release command.
